艾米莉亚·克拉克 (Emilia Clarke) 认为她会因脑损伤而被《权力的游戏》解雇https://www.nme.com/news/tv/emilia-clarke-thought-shed-be-fired-from-game-of-thrones-after-brain-injury-3764134?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=emilia-克拉克认为因脑损伤而因《权力的游戏》而被解雇Alex BerryMon, 10 Jun 2024 12:26:17 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3764134 <p><img width="1377" height="875" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾米莉亚·克拉克" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones.jpg 1377w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1377px) 100vw, 1377px" /></p><p>这位演员在拍摄 HBO 剧集时两次失血</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/emilia-clarke-thought-shed-be-fired-from-game-of-thrones-after-brain-injury-3764134">艾米莉亚·克拉克 (Emilia Clarke) 认为脑损伤后她会被《权力的游戏》解雇的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1377" height="875" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾米莉亚·克拉克" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones.jpg 1377w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-1068x679.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1377px) 100vw, 1377px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/emilia-clarke">艾米莉亚·克拉克</a>表示，她认为自己可能因严重脑损伤而被<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/game-of-thrones"><em>《权力的游戏》</em></a>解雇。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/house-of-the-dragon-review-game-of-thrones-3293830">《龙之屋》评论：《权力的游戏》传奇继续保持风格</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位在热门奇幻剧集中饰演丹妮莉丝·坦格利安的演员于 2011 年遭遇脑出血。</p><p>她在 2019 年<a href="https://www.newyorker.com/culture/personal-history/emilia-clarke-a-battle-for-my-life-brain-aneurysm-surgery-game-of-thrones" target="_blank" rel="noopener">为<em>《纽约客》</em>撰写的一篇文章</a>中透露，她在 2011 年 2 月经历了因动脉瘤破裂引起的蛛网膜下腔出血。结果，她接受了血管内弹簧圈栓塞手术，据报道暂时无法说出自己的名字。</p><p> 2013 年，她还因第二次动脉瘤接受了手术治疗。这两起事件发生时，这位演员仍在拍摄<em>《权力的游戏》</em> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3764157" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3764157" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3764157" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-2.jpg" alt="艾米莉亚·克拉克" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Emilia-clarke-game-of-thrones-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3764157" class="wp-caption-text">艾米莉亚·克拉克在《权力的游戏》中饰演丹妮莉丝·坦格利安。图片来源：HBO/天空电视台</figcaption></figure><p>现在，克拉克透露，她当时担心自己的病情可能会影响她的职业生涯。这位演员在<a href="https://www.bigissue.com/culture/emilia-clarke-brain-injury-sameyou-game-of-thrones/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《The Big Issue》</em></a>的新封面采访中说道：“我们所有人的第一个恐惧是：‘天哪，我会被解雇吗？我会因为他们认为我无法完成工作而被解雇吗？”</p><p>她分享了这段经历：“当你脑部受伤时，因为它会极大地改变你的自我意识，你进入工作场所的所有不安全感会在一夜之间增加四倍。”</p><p>据报道，她的大出血发生在<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/hbo">HBO</a>剧集拍摄期间，因此一开始她能够相对保密自己的病情。她谈到了制作该节目的庞大团队及其庞大而忠实的观众：“好吧，如果我要死，我最好死在电视直播中。”</p><p>在采访的其他地方，克拉克谈到了她对自己病情的不安全感，以及她和母亲于 2019 年创立的慈善机构 SameYou。</p><p>她分享道：“慢性病会削弱你对生活的信心，这让你变得如此虚弱和孤独。” “脑损伤给我带来的最大感受就是极度孤独。这就是我们正在努力克服的问题。”</p><p>其他消息方面， <em>《权力的游戏》</em>衍生剧<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/house-of-the-dragon"><em>《龙之屋》</em></a>第二季将于 6 月 16 日首播，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/critics-praise-violent-and-gorgeous-second-season-of-house-of-the-dragon-3763721">获得了评论家的积极早期评价</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/emilia-clarke-thought-shed-be-fired-from-game-of-thrones-after-brain-injury-3764134">艾米莉亚·克拉克 (Emilia Clarke) 认为脑损伤后她会被《权力的游戏》解雇的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
